title: Josh Bedford presents the etnies X Mutiny collection
description:
Etnies proudly presents the etnies x Mutiny collection. BMX is a brotherhood. We stick together, we support one another and we ride. We have grown up on our BMX, we live it, we love it. These words where the base of what brought etnies and Mutiny bikes together and Josh Bedford the glue which made this collaboration one. Mutiny was a result of cynicism about the industry. Mutiny wanted to be an instrument of change in the industry and this is exactly where the etnies x Mutiny product stand for.
Find out more on the etnies Mutiny collaboration here: etnies.com/blog/2012/10/21/josh-bedford-presents-the-etnies-x-mutiny-collection/
